      "comment": "ANGRY FRIENDSHIP (4) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (20.97) at this track over 365m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can measure up this time. ROMANI LASS (3) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 365m behind Zipping Babe (21.18) in a Grade 5. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can measure up this time. SKEDADDLE DENNIS (2) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the money last time though when third (21.22) at this track. Solid record here winning three races. Can feature again. ASHBY TEX (6) has been freshened and can sneak into the frame on his best form.",
